<title type="html"><![CDATA[2/12.Oregon man lives in a Boeing 727, wants to build another airplane home in Japan]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=700&amp;p=728#p728"><![CDATA[
Host: Jennie Topics for discussion on Feb. 12<br /><br />Session one:  Oregon man lives in a Boeing 727, wants to build another airplane home in Japan <br /><br />1. After read the article, please share your thoughts on the dream house that Bruce Campbell owns?<br />2. Do you have any dreams that you would like to fulfill one day?   Please share with us if any.<br /> 3. In order to fulfill your costly dream but impacts your lifestyle severely, will you <br />usually insist, hesitate or just give it up?<br /><br />4. Have you ever had regrets about giving up your dream when you were young?<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.seattlepi.com/lifestyle/article/Oregon-man-lives-in-an-Boeing-727-wants-to-build-6840951.php">https://www.seattlepi.com/lifestyle/art ... 840951.php</a><!-- m --><br />Session two: <br />What to know about BNPL(Buy Now Pay Later)<br /> <br />1. Will you take BNPL into consideration when make purchases?  If yes, why?<br /><br />2. How do you think that BNPL jeopardizes those who are financially naive?<br /><br />3. What are the pros and cons of BNPL for retailers and consumers?<br /><br />4. Free talk about your consuming habits.  <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/lang/archives/2022/09/20/2003785582">https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/lang/a ... 2003785582</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 p.m Individual Presentation<br />8：00-8：40 Group Discussion <br />8:40-9:00 p.m<br />Individual Presentation<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">dora</a> — Mon Feb 06, 2023 7:52 am</p><hr />
